# Slide 1 — Title

## AI-Assisted Rules Knowledge System

### 20-Day Proof of Concept

**Objective**

Demonstrate that AI can convert a **40-year-old rules engine** into a **transparent, queryable knowledge system** without modifying production.

**Artifacts analyzed**

* Mapping tables
* Legacy code (C / COBOL)
* Historical transactions

**Outcome**

Build a **Canonical Rule Model (IR)** enabling rule explanation, lineage tracing, and automated documentation.

---

### Speaker Notes

We are proposing a short proof of concept to see whether modern AI techniques can help us extract and structure the knowledge embedded in our rules engine.
The idea is not to change the system — only to build a **knowledge layer that understands it**.

