# Slide 3 — Rule Graph

## Converting Mapping Tables into Rule Chains

```mermaid
flowchart LR

A[Subledger Record]

B[Mapping Rule
Product → Category]

C[Allocation Rule
Allocate by Desk]

D[Distribution Rule
Split by Cost Center]

E[GL Posting]

A --> B
